is went on for about three years, and Ketchup Caddy got about $1 million of=
 capacity payments. The fake customers got nothing. Also, no harm, no foul,=
 ish:
Because MISO did not call a curtailment event in any of these Planning Year=
s and required only mock tests to verify performance, Ketchup Caddy=E2=80=
=99s false registrations and offers did not come to light until Staff=E2=80=
=99s Investigation.
They sold fake power capacity to the grid for three years, but nobody notic=
ed, because they were never called on to deliver that power.=C2=A0
Anyway, great fraud. Apparently Meinershagen was totally innocent:
Unlike Mango, Staff found no evidence that Meinershagen was expressly aware=
