 the UAE or Masayoshi Son or whomever and are like =E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m loo=
king for $7 trillion,=E2=80=9D maybe that will anchor their expectations hi=
gh enough that they=E2=80=99re like =E2=80=9Cwell we can=E2=80=99t do that,=
 but we=E2=80=99re in for a more modest ticket, would $7 billion help,=E2=
=80=9D and then you=E2=80=99ve got $7=C2=A0billion, which is actually a lot=
.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">It fits nicely with Altman=E2=80=
=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34493478.2853=
