=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
 other strategy</a>=C2=A0of suggesting that AI, if mishandled, could destro=
y humanity: That self-aggrandizing claim is more plausible if it also comes=
 with an enormous price tag.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">It=E2=
=80=99s gotta help with recruiting, throwing around numbers like that.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">OpenAI is a relatively young company (and <a h=
ref=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34493478.285379/aHR0cH=
M6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTEtMjcvb3BlbmFpL=
WlzLXN0aWxsLWFuLTg2LWJpbGxpb24tbm9ucHJvZml0P2NtcGlkPUJCRDAyMjcyNF9NT05FWVNU=
VUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDI=
